videos.description: Kihei Clark drains a 3-pointer from the corner, then steals the inbounds pass and finds Kyle Guy for another long-ball to give the Cavaliers an early lead.
videos.headline: Clark scores, steals and assists for back-to-back triples

videos.description: Ty Jerome gets into the paint and lobs it up for De'Andre Hunter, who puts away a strong two-handed alley-oop.
videos.headline: Jerome lobs, Hunter slams

videos.description: Brandon Robinson denies Kihei Clark on the inside, then Coby White runs the floor and finishes with a tough layup off the glass.
videos.headline: Robinson's big block leads to White's finish

videos.description: Cameron Johnson picks up the loose ball and takes it the other way, finishing through contact with a tough transition layup for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Johnson goes coast-to-coast for and-1

videos.description: Garrison Brooks gets the steal and Luke Maye sends a long pass to Cameron Johnson, who finishes the go-ahead layup early in the second half.
videos.headline: Tar Heels take lead on Johnson's fast-break finish

videos.description: Ty Jerome swings a pass to Kyle Guy, who drains a huge 3-ball through contact to extend Virginia's late-game lead and earn himself a 4-point play opportunity.
videos.headline: Guy hits clutch 3 late in game
